dc_title_s: Amplissimae regionis Mississipi seu provinciae Ludoviciana
dc_description_s: 1 map : hand col. ; 47 x 56 cm|Shows United States west to New Mexico, parts of Canada and Mexico.|Shows routes of various explorers to 1716.|Cartouche in upper right surrounding title and view of Niagra Falls.|Includes cartouche enclosing a bison with two Native Americans, an opossum and a pelican in lower right.|Relief shown by hachures and pictorially.
